name: Tutti Campioni della Scuola con il Nuovo Conoscere Insieme
Yoghi tra le Meraviglie di Gardaland

description: Redención, Mexico. It is a sort of Shan-gri-là of crime populated with criminals on the run. They hope to live in luxury, surrounded by beautiful women, but the city belongs to the cruel El Jefe, who takes possession of their money and exploits them, preventing them from leaving the city. That is, until Mister No arrives in Redención …
name: Uno Straniero a Redención

description: It’s time for the showdown between Mister No and El Jefe, the gangland boss of Redención who has kidnapped Barrett, Jerry’s old friend, and who tortures those who oppose him by subjecting them to the arts of a crazy Nazistoid doctor. Ishikawa himself also arrives in Redención, and this marks a turning point in his relationship with Mister No…
name: Terra Senza Legge

description: The border between Mexico and the United States. Crossing it is a goal ardently craved by many desperados, willing to do anything to enter “The Land of Opportunity”. Among these, strangely enough, is Mister No, whose documents have been confiscated by the CIA. And he will discover the sinister side of the frontier police…
name: Frontiera

description: Fred Adams is a dreamer. He makes crazy horror and science-fiction films with ridiculous special effects and absurd plots. He is making one in the marshes of Louisiana and persuades Mister No to act in it. But tragedy looms over the set…
name: Il Mostro della Palude

description: Osceola National Forest, Florida. Here, Mister No meets his friend the ranger Alan Chambers, who is doing a refresher course on fighting against forest fires. But sometimes technology is useless…A furious fire breaks out, some tourists are trapped in the forest, and only Mister No can save them!
name: Uragano di Fuoco

description: Georgia. Two criminals, Morgan Ballard and Werner Smith escape from “Death row” and hijack a bus on which Mister No is traveling, slaughtering many innocent civilians. It’s a death trip!
name: Un Giorno da Cani

description: A city with no name, literally possessed by the powerful gangster Temistocles Zard. A journalist who attempts to stand up to him. A dark lady, ambiguous and attractive. A newspaper director with Japanese origins and a dark past, and Mister No who defies Zard and his men…
name: Dark City

description: Bartlesville, in Virginia, is a provincial centre, dull and sanctimonious. Mister No travels there with Hank Brooks, ex country star, who is returning to his native city. But an old lover is waiting for him, thirsty for revenge…
name: Il Seme dell'Odio

description: Susan Stillman, the powerful “lady”, has bought Bartlesville: the whole town cooperates in murdering Hank Brooks (and murdering Mister No as well, who tries to save him), because years ago Hank seduced and then abandoned her. Perhaps there is still hope for our men…
name: La Condanna

description: Mike, Mister No’s new friend, is willing to do anything to race in Formula Indy. He is heavily in debt and to meet the payments he consents to committing a robbery with three brothers. Who, however want to use him as a scapegoat…
name: Dietro la Maschera

description: Mister No finally returns to the Big Apple, the city where he was born, and it is here that the final encounter with Ishikawa is waiting for him. But he gets involved in a veritable war between the Japanese, Don Salvatore’s mobsters (who are seeking revenge for the murder of one of their ringleaders, a certain Carducci, committed by Ishikawa) and the CIA!
name: Ritorno a New York

description: Mobsters and Japanese fight in New York. Mister No and Ishikawa are momentarily on the same side, fighting against the Mob. After defeating their adversaries, the pair will square up for the final showdown…
name: L'Ombra del Nemico

description:
It's hot - unbearably hot. The sun glares down from the sky like molten brass. The metal of the gun you clutch so tightly scorches your hand.

You flick away the sweat that trickles into your eyes, for you mustn't miss the slightest stir of a bush - it might hide a Jap sniper whose next bullet could have your name on it.

There's war in the jungle.

And then there's those hectic bursts of savage action when it's every man for himself and the Japs take the hindmost!
name: Blood River

description:
Armed to the teeth, they slipped and slithered from the hull of a submarine into a wave-battered rubber dinghy.

A grim cargo of trouble on a life-or-death mission.

Ten desperate men who were to become...

... Ten Dauntless Heroes!
name: Cold Steel

description:
When a platoon of front line soldiers earn the nickname 'Yellow-Bellies' they can only rid themselves of it by fighting like supermen.

Here, then, is the story of one such platoon, and of how on the bullet-swept slopes of an Italian hill they grabbed desperately at the chance to get rid of that yellow smear.

Hill 13 it was called officially, but to the heroic 'Yellow-Bellies' it will always be 'Dead Man's Hill'...
name: Hill 13

description:
Red is the colour of courage.

Like the ribbon of the Victoria Cross; like the blood that heroes spill; like the famous Red Beret of the Parachute Regiment, whose amazing story this is.

Meet in these pages Cobber Kane, tough, wise-cracking Australian; Sgt. Jim Parker, steady as a rock; 'Blood n' Guts' Sanders, the hard-bitten R.S.M., whose one aim in battle was a V.C. to pin next to his M.M... the kind of heroes who have made the Red beret the badge of courage it is...
name: Gun Fury
